<?xml version="1.0" encoding="windows-1251"?>

<Modul UId="AEBYN5YL7F9ZQJHMXFOL" Level="1" ADate="ET77IJ9X" Author="Волосатова">
<Title>Примеры базисных функций</Title>
<P><Font Color="#0000FF">1.</Font> Импульсные</P>
<P><Formula Br="Y" Num="Y" ID="EU74F8YC">&#x3C6;<Sub>k</Sub>=rect(t&#x2212;kT)/T</Formula></P>
<P><Formula>rect(t)=<LogBr><M X="0.0" Y="1.25" Kh="1.25">{</M><M X="1.25" Y="1.12" Kh="1.0"><Matrix Col="1" Row="2" Alg="1"><M X="0.5" Y="1.2" Kh="1.0">1  0&#x227C;(t)&#x227C;1</M><M X="0.5" Y="2.6" Kh="1.0">0 в противном случае</M></Matrix></M><Z X="2.25" Y="1.25" Kh="1.25" /></LogBr></Formula></P>
<P><Formula>U<Sub>k</Sub>=<Fraction><M>1</M><M>T</M></Fraction><Limits><M>(k+1)t</M><M>&#x222B;</M><M>kT</M></Limits>U(t)dt</Formula></P>
<P><Font Color="#0000FF">2.</Font> Гармонические (экспоненциальные)</P>
<P><Formula Br="Y" Num="Y" ID="EU74I0IE">&#x3C6;<Sub>k</Sub>(t)=sin(<Fraction><M>&#x3C0;kt</M><M>T</M></Fraction>)&#x3C0;,</Formula></P>
<P><Formula>&#x3C6;<Sub>k</Sub>(t)=exp(<Fraction><M>&#x3AF;&#x3C0;kt</M><M>T</M></Fraction>),</Formula></P>
<P><Formula>U<Sub>k</Sub>=<Fraction><M>1</M><M>2T</M></Fraction><Matrix Col="1" Row="3" Alg="1"><M X="0.5" Y="1.2" Kh="1.0">T</M><M X="0.5" Y="2.6" Kh="1.0">&#x222B;</M><M X="0.5" Y="4.0" Kh="1.0">0</M></Matrix>U(t)exp(<Fraction><M>&#x2212;&#x3AF;&#x3C0;kt</M><M>T</M></Fraction>)dt</Formula></P>
<P><Font Color="#0000FF">3.</Font> Функции отсчетов</P>
<P><Formula Br="Y" Num="Y" ID="EU74I8YP">&#x3C6;<Sub>k</Sub>(t)=sinc2&#x3C0;T<Fraction><M>t&#x2212;k</M><M>2T</M></Fraction></Formula></P>
<P><Formula>sincx=<Fraction><M>sinc(x)</M><M>x</M></Fraction></Formula></P>
<P><Formula>U<Sub>k</Sub>=<Fraction><M>1</M><M>2T</M></Fraction><Matrix Col="1" Row="3" Alg="1"><M X="0.5" Y="1.2" Kh="1.0">+&#x221D;</M><M X="0.5" Y="2.6" Kh="1.0">&#x222B;</M><M X="7.26" Y="5.14" Kh="1.0">&#x2212;&#x221D;</M></Matrix>U(t)sinc[<Fraction><M>t&#x2212;k</M><M>2T</M></Fraction>2&#x3C0;T]dt=U<Fraction><M>k</M><M>2T</M></Fraction></Formula></P>
<P><Font Color="#0000FF">4.</Font> Функция Уолша</P>
<P><Formula>Wal<Sub>k</Sub>(&#x3BE;)=<Fraction><M>1</M><M>&#x221A;T</M></Fraction>(&#x2212;1)</Formula><Sup><Limits><Z X="3.26" Y="0.67" Kh="0.8" /><M X="0.0" Y="2.15" Kh="0.8"><Matrix Col="1" Row="3" Alg="0"><M X="0.39" Y="0.96" Kh="0.8">&#x221D;</M><M X="0.39" Y="2.08" Kh="0.8">&#x2211;</M><M X="0.39" Y="3.2" Kh="0.8">m=0</M></Matrix>K<Matrix Col="1" Row="2" Alg="1"><M X="0.39" Y="0.96" Kh="0.8">Г</M><M X="0.39" Y="2.08" Kh="0.8">m</M></Matrix>&#x3BE;<Sub>m+1</Sub></M><M X="3.15" Y="3.82" Kh="0.8" /></Limits></Sup></P>
<P>где <Formula>&#x3BE;=<Fraction><M>t</M><M>T</M></Fraction>; &#x3BE;=<Limits><M>&#x221D;</M><M>&#x2211;</M><M>m=0</M></Limits>&#x3BE;<Sub>m+1</Sub>2<Sup>-(m+1)</Sup></Formula>- двоичное представление числа &#x3BE;</P>
<P><Formula>K<Matrix Col="1" Row="3" Alg="1"><M X="0.5" Y="1.2" Kh="1.0">r</M><M X="0.5" Y="2.6" Kh="1.0" /><M X="0.5" Y="4.0" Kh="1.0">m</M></Matrix>=k<Sub>m</Sub>&#x2295;k<Sub>m+1</Sub></Formula> m-й разряд кода Грея номера k.</P>
<P>k<Sub>m</Sub>- m-й номер двоичного разряда числа k (справа налево)</P>
<P><Formula>k=<Matrix Col="1" Row="3" Alg="1"><M X="0.5" Y="1.2" Kh="1.0">&#x221D;</M><M X="0.5" Y="2.6" Kh="1.0">&#x2211;</M><M X="0.5" Y="4.0" Kh="1.0">m=0</M></Matrix>k<Sub>m</Sub>2<Sup>m</Sup>, &#x2295; </Formula>&#x2014; сложение по модулю 2.</P>
<P>Пример функций Уолша:</P>
